creator: MonBuilding&Co
descriptionHtml:
Join the app of your building and enjoy many services directly from your mobile.

MonBuilding is a simple, practical & secure application to stay informed and communicate within a building.

The application allows you to :
- follow what's happening in your building in real-time, with your building's news and incidents' reporting
- to chat with other building's occupants via messenger or a forum
- benefit from services to simplify your daily life: concierge services, reservation of common areas or goods, parcel delivery, and all other third-party services integrated into the app.
descriptionShort: Join the app of your building and enjoy many services directly from your mobile.
